description: These Cruisetag luggage holders from Specialist ID are a must have essential for any cruiser. Perfect fit for printed eTags for Princess, Carnival, Costa, Holland America and Norwegian Cruise Tags. You just print and fold the document as directed and insert into our sturdy 3 1/4" X 6" pouch sleeve. Wrap the loop through (and attach to your luggage) and you're good to go. Now there's no more worry about paper tags tearing and luggage being misplaced and no need for tape or a stapler to get the job done! Besides your handy lanyard and key card holder, luggage tie tags make the cut for top accessories to have on cruises. With clear visibility of your cruise information listed on your baggage, staff can better direct your luggage to your cabin without delays. They work best when hanging on the outside of your luggage. Available in economical bulk packs, they make great gift ideas for cruisers or for travel agents to offer their clients, but also ideal to have a set handy for you and your family for all your documents needed while cruising. Since vinyl plastic is waterproof, these card holders will be long lasting for your travel vacation ticket needs. These 9 inch size worm loops are flexible and bendable to loop around your luggage bag handle yet durable and strong enough to give a secure hold while traveling and on the go. They really are a great travel accessory for all your ship tag labels needed for identification. The convenient slot punch holes allow to be used with any lanyard, badge reel clip or neck chain to easily wear over a shirt or other types of clothing when not looped around a travel bag. Perfect for carrying your big baggage identifiers or packing supplies. Great Attachment ideas include name tags, a fragile sticker, funny pictures, your initial, or some smart saying. These are great not only for cruising, but also for labeling you clothing in storage, or items you need for your fleet of work trucks, boat registration and more.
